{"tid":1259754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請將互屌嘅精力擺番去對狗對政府對藍屍，諗下有咩可以做好過好，好似之前出長輩圖個陣咁","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T16:13:58.000Z","uid":35776,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edd09095c95b7b307f5f4a64b0ede36c7bbfec95","tid":1259754,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"pro泛民 pro熱普城 pro本土 都好<br />\n老土D講<br />\n係度互屌只會畀機會五毛乘虛而入<br />\n以假亂真咁拉人落泥漿摔角<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>所謂分化唔需要用錢收買</strong></span><br />\n只要令你地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不斷增加牙齒印加新仇舊恨</span></span>，效果比收買一百個人都大<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>所以我懇請各門各派 將牙齒印放一邊</strong></span> <br />\n不如諗下仲有咩路線可以做，需要做<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">減少自己人犯錯 增加政府犯錯機會<br />\n</span></strong>請大家再度回想6.9 以來嘅做法<br />\n我地<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">方法不同，但目標一致</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>覺得有需要批評嘅，就限於批評提點</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一人做多步 目標好快到</span></span><br />\n繼續爬山 不割席 不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f006e36ad3e0c4ced2df8a2e4e07429da2c970e","tid":1259754,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"推          <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-a